name: People Series
description: It has been about 15 years since I started painting. In the past 10 years, I’ve conducted a personal project that contains a series of portraits. In these paintings I have captured the essence of particular moments or a gaze of a person that has impressed me at first glance. Size: 2800px - 2000px Technique: Charcoal and Conte on Heavy Kraft Paper - ————————>>>> Due to a technical issue with the Hick At Nanak website, this work as well as 22 other works by me have been hacked stolen  . I posses sufficient documentation to suggest that my account has been hacked. Also, I have received no response from the Hic et nunc website despite several attempts to contact. As a result I have decided to reload this work.
